1. *Leđa* su mu bila okrenuta prema prozoru. (His back was turned towards the window.)

2. *Leđima* je šetao ulicom. (He was walking down the street with his back.)

3. *Leđima* je bacio svoj kaput. (He threw his coat over his back.)

4. *Leđima* je stavio svoju torbu. (He put his bag on his back.) 

5. *Leđa* mu se naježila od straha. (His back bristled with fear.)